<BaseLayout
  title="About — Sparkes Mobile Detailing"
  description="Small, owner-operated mobile detailing serving East Tennessee from Knoxville to Bristol."
>
  <div class="page about">
    <div class="bubble-field" id="about-bubbles"></div>

    <h1>We treat your car<br/>like <em>ours</em>.</h1>

    <p class="about-lede">
      Sparkes is a small, owner-operated mobile detailing outfit serving
      East Tennessee from Knoxville to Bristol.
      One van, one obsessive crew, no upsells.
    </p>

    <div class="grid-2">
      <div class="about-block">
        <h3>The story</h3>
        <p>
          We started Sparkes after years of cringing at automated tunnels and
          "express" details that left holograms on every clear coat. The
          premise is simple: bring the standards of a concours prep shop to
          the customer's driveway, and never rush the job.
        </p>
        <p>
          Today we look after a curated list of clients — track and rally
          drivers, cars &amp; coffee regulars, and yes, a few garage queens —
          across East Tennessee. Most come back. We work by one-off
          appointment, or on a standing weekly or monthly schedule for clients
          who want us on rotation.
        </p>
        <h3 style="margin-top: 28px;">What "high-end" means here</h3>
        <p>
          We're set up for paint that matters. Single-stage lacquer, ceramic
          coatings, satin PPF, raw carbon — all handled with the right pads,
          the right pH and a lot of patience. If you're not sure your car
          qualifies, send a photo and we'll tell you straight.
        </p>
      </div>

      <aside class="specs">
        <ul>
          <li><div><b>Service area.</b> East Tennessee from Knoxville to Bristol. Storage facilities and trailer pickup welcome.</div></li>
          <li><div><b>Water &amp; power.</b> Onboard 100-gal tank, 2.5kW inverter. No hookups required.</div></li>
          <li><div><b>Booking cadence.</b> Weekly, fortnightly, monthly maintenance — or one-off pre-event prep.</div></li>
          <li><div><b>Coatings.</b> Authorized for Gyeon Quartz and CQuartz UK 3.0. 2–7 yr durability tiers.</div></li>
          <li><div><b>Insurance.</b> $2M public liability, $500K care, custody &amp; control.</div></li>
          <li><div><b>What we don't do.</b> Compounds on soft Japanese clears without a paint reading. Drive-thru speeds. Tire shine slingshots.</div></li>
        </ul>
      </aside>
    </div>

